<h3>About TopQ</h3>
<p>Founded in 2005, TopQ played a crucial part in the local transformation of the field of test automation – from codeless QA to pure development using open source solutions – with its introduction of JSystem.</p>
<p>TopQ has since continued to release innovative open-source test automation solutions. Acquired by Matrix I.T. in 2014, TopQ further expanded.</p>
<p>With a team of a 120 developers and 13 years of experience in over 500 successfully completed projects, TopQ leads the field of development based test automation solutions in Israel – seamlessly integrating in every sector and technology.</p>
